Writing a working CronJob YAML manifest
Using command blocks in containers
Volume mounts in pods (hostPath usage)
Managing backup logic inside containerized scripts
ðŸ‘€ I followed along with an excellent YouTube session on Kubernetes and took a hands-on approach to make the learning stick. Hereâ€™s a quick look at my terminal setup during the learning process:
